sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER , PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.CATEGORY FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 ON PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 381 ;
